OL,3,CMum horrified by cost of Christmas
OL,4,Cevents puts on her own
OL,6,FA Somerset mother has organised her
OL,7,Fown Christmas event for a town after
OL,8,Fbeing horrified by how much other
OL,9,Fattractions in the region cost.
OL,11,FEmma Cole, along with her husband
OL,12,FEdward, have created Bridgwater
OL,13,FChristmas Sparkle, which will be on
OL,14,Funtil 1st January.
OL,16,FThe event is being held at Blake
OL,17,FGardens in the town centre and
OL,18,Ffeatures skating, rides, food and
OL,19,Fentertainment.
