OL,3,CMum horrified by cost of Christmas
OL,4,Cevents puts on her own
OL,6,FEmma said: "Myself and my husband are
OL,7,Ffrom several generations of showmen
OL,8,Ffamilies so we are entertainers and
OL,9,Fthat's what we do for a living.
OL,11,F"What we wanted to do here - not
OL,12,Feverybody can afford #100 to get on a
OL,13,Ftrain to go to Bristol to go skating
OL,14,For see Santa. We've tried to make
OL,15,Fsomething safe, fun, affordable and
OL,16,Fexciting for Bridgwater, for the town,
OL,17,Ffor the people."
